WEBVTT

00:00:00.156 --> 00:00:01.556
Al Gore: COP26,

00:00:01.556 --> 00:00:05.356
the Conference of the Parties
on the climate treaty,

00:00:05.356 --> 00:00:09.036
is where every nation
in the world comes together

00:00:09.036 --> 00:00:11.636
to negotiate collective action

00:00:11.636 --> 00:00:13.076
to solve the climate crisis.

00:00:13.196 --> 00:00:14.716
Christiana Figueres: COP26,

00:00:14.716 --> 00:00:16.836
which is the one that is coming up now,

00:00:16.836 --> 00:00:18.236
in Glasgow,

00:00:18.236 --> 00:00:22.756
is the 26th time that these governments
are getting together

00:00:22.756 --> 00:00:25.876
to do, frankly, follow-up
to the Paris Agreement.

00:00:26.556 --> 00:00:28.916
They need to come to the table

00:00:28.916 --> 00:00:33.476
to report to each other
what they have done since Paris,